            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>fiery chicken</strong></p><p>Once cooked, remove the pan from the heat and reserve the oil in the pan – this is your <strong>spicy oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
