    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s] </strong>in half lengthways, around the<strong> </strong>stone[s]</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and mash roughly</p>",
