    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove the <strong>outer leaves</strong> and shred the <strong>inner core[s]</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
