    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>mashed avocado</strong> and<strong> diced shallot</strong> to a bowl with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>coriander </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>avocado salsa</strong></p>",
