    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>fiery chicken</strong> on a clean board and serve it over the <strong>coriander rice </strong>with the <strong>lettuce leaves</strong> to the side</p><p>Spoon over the <strong>avocado salsa </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>spicy oil</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
